reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 17, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars The best invention!
reviews.reviewText: It's strong! Got 3 speeds and the forcible legs have literally been a game changer! I've brought it with me on a train, in the hospital, at a hotel, air bnb, family member houses and I can attach it practically anywhere! Just make sure you remember that the highest speed makes the battery drain faster, so it will need plugged in sooner! So, my only thing is wish it had a bigger battery, lol, but it still lasts hours, and you can use it while it's plugged in also, and it takes the same charger as my phone, a type c, so I just switch my phone back and forth with this fan!! I just love it!

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars *Edited Review* Good Fan & Great Customer Service
reviews.reviewText: I left a negative review on this product because I thought that the fan broke after a month of use. It turns out it was just the charger I replaced the charger and it’s working great. In response to my review the seller reached out to me with a number of opportunities to replace the fan at no cost to me. They were persistent in making sure that I was satisfied with my purchase and because of that I came back to edit my review to make sure that their product is properly reflected. I would recommend this product and the seller I purchased it from!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 15, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Works great on my C.O.W
reviews.reviewText: I use this fan on my CoW (Computers on Wheels) at work when I’m passing medications. As a nurse on the go all the time, this fan keeps me cool all day during medication passes or my hot flashes! The different power settings are also nice for low, intermediate, or high activity. The legs are sturdy and bend at different angles to grip onto the COW. As for the battery life, it depends on how much you use and the power level. The nice thing about having the USB plug is I don’t have to worry about it dying on me while it’s plugged in during high activity.My coworkers also said the fan is useful on baby strollers. Versatile and effective fan - can’t go wrong with it. 👍
